pport","cookieWarning-accept":"accept","cookieWarning-dialogTitle":"Cookie settings","dynamicFeeTable-feeColumnTitle":"Withdrawal fee","dynamicFeeTable-minimumColumnTitle":"Withdrawal minimum (including fee)","dynamicFeeTable-nameColumnTitle":"Cryptocurrency","menu-createAccount":"Sign up","menu-contactUs":"Contact Us","menu-myActivities":"My activities","menu-signIn":"Sign in","menu-signOut":"Sign out","error-backTo":"Back to Support","error-reload":"Reload page","error-subtitle":"Our server encountered an internal server error. Please try again.","error-title":"Sorry, this page is not working right now","dlt-homeLink":"Visit Kraken","searchBar-needHelpContent":"\u003cp\u003eNeed help? Checkout our \u003cCustom.ExternalLink key=\"8e1cbcbdca58\"\u003eself-service guides\u003c/Custom.ExternalLink\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","homepage-appsHeading":"Browse by product","homepage-apps-03b5615d77f1-name":" Pro","homepage-apps-03b5615d77f1-description":"A professional trading experience on the go","homepage-apps-4378c97f1621-name":"Desktop","homepage-apps-4378c97f1621-description":"Turn your Mac or PC into a super-charged trading station","homepage-apps-42083249994f-name":"Wallet","homepage-apps-42083249994f-description":"Securely store and manage your crypto and NFTs","config-recommendedSearches-depositing-crypto ":"depositing crypto ","config-recommendedSearches-withdrawing-crypto":"withdrawing crypto","config-recommendedSearches-deposit-fees":"deposit fees","config-recommendedSearches-withdrawal-fees":"withdrawal fees","config-recommendedSearches-two-factor-authentication ":"two-factor authentication ","config-recommendedSearches-verification":"verification","dlt-redirect-drawer-title":"Oops! It looks like you're unable to view this content from Germany.","dlt-redirect-drawer-content":"\u003cp\u003eDon’t worry, we’ve got you covered.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo access this page and explore more, please visit our dedicated German site to discover exciting content tailored for you.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you believe this detection is an error, please close and navigate back.\u003c/p\u003e","dlt-redirect-drawer-confirmText":"Access German Site","article-4844359082772-title":"Linear Multi-Collateral Derivatives Contract Specifications","article-4844359082772-content":"\u003cp\u003eBelow you can find three sections with detailed information on Kraken\u0026#x27;s linear multi-collateral perpetual and fixed maturity derivatives contracts. \u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eClick to expand each section: \u003c/p\u003e\u003cCustom.AccordionList key=\"LVQCEduka53puUQ_dMBZ5\"\u003e\u003cCustom.AccordionListItem key=\"85Bl7Ei4pF_CN0GWYSZ59\"\u003e\u003cCustom.AccordionListItemTitle\u003ePerpetual Contract Specifications\u003c/Custom.AccordionListItemTitle\u003e\u003cCustom.AccordionListItemContent\u003e\u003cp\u003ePerpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have \u003cstrong\u003eno expiration date\u003c/strong\u003e and an \u003cstrong\u003eauto-rolling\u003c/strong\u003e feature \u003cstrong\u003eevery hour\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePerpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract\u0026#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset\u0026#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under \u0026quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information\u0026quot; in the next drop-down menu. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMargin Class\u003c/strong\u003e and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in \u003cCustom.ArticleLink key=\"252c68b51eca\"\u003eDerivatives Margin Schedule \u0026amp; Maximum Leverage\u003c/Custom.ArticleLink\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cCustom.Callout key=\"W5AGGl2S4TGrGX6eYooG3\"\u003e\u003cCustom.CalloutTitle\u003ePlease note:\u003c/Custom.CalloutTitle\u003e\u003cCustom.CalloutMessage\u003e\u003cp\u003eDelisted and settled contracts are archived \u003cCustom.ExternalLink key=\"f4963a3f23adc\"\u003ehere\u003c/Custom.ExternalLink\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.CalloutMessage\u003e\u003c/Custom.Callout\u003e\u003cCustom.Table key=\"ZS9QA8BxKk4ehHnYaytAe\"\u003e\u003cCustom.TableRow\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSymbol\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBase Currency\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMin Lot\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTick Size\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003eMax Position (Base)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003eImpact Mid (Base)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003eMargin Class \u0026amp; Max Leverage\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFirst Trading\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableRow\u003e\u003cCustom.TableRow\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003ePF_1INCHUSD\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e1inch (1INCH)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e1\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e0.0001\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e6,000,000\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e12000 1INCH\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003eClass C (25x)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003cCustom.TableCell\u003e\u003cp\u003e24-Aug-2022\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableCell\u003e\u003c/Custom.TableRow\u